			"description": "I was walking in a park looking for subjects to photograph when suddenly i spot a bird watching me. First I got stressed that I might miss the shot. But when i started taking pictures this little bird just became a perfect model. The bird was very curious, approaching very close and looking directly at the camera. I was lucky enough to get A LOT of shots, but these one are my favorite. The photos were taken during winter in Belgium so the weather was really cloudy and dark",
